
See http://data.worldbank.org/developers

Procedure
=========

# Start with getting the vocabularies:

  cd scripts
  sh get.vocs.sh
  sh get.indicators.sh
  sh create.rdf.indicators.indicator.en.sh
  sh create.rdf.void.sh

Currencies and countries

Countries:
http://www.iso.org/iso/home/standards/country_codes/country_names_and_code_elements_xml.htm

Currencies:
http://www.currency-iso.org/content/dam/isocy/downloads/dl_iso_table_a1.xml

It looks like the country names can be matched to currencies and codes by using these two tables.
